[section#exec.snd.transform
    [`execution::transform_sender]
]

[%@lib transform_sender]
[codeblock:declaration]
namespace std::execution {
  template<[[redoc("`:c>")]]sender Sndr, [[redoc("*:c>")]]queryable Env>
    constexpr decltype(auto) transform_sender(Sndr&& sndr, const Env& env)
      noexcept([[redoc("[=seebelow]")]]);
}
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] For a subexpression [`s], let [*start-domain] be [`D()] where [`D] is the
decayed type of [`get_domain(env)] if that expression is well-formed, and
[`default_domain] otherwise.
[:zh_CN] 对于子表达式 [`s]，令 [*start-domain] 为 [`D()]，其中如果表达式
[`get_domain(env)] 良构，则 [`D] 是该表达式的退化类型；否为 [`default_domain]。

[para]
[:en] Let [`[*completion-domain](s)] be [`D()] where [`D] is the decayed type of
[`get_completion_domain<>(get_env(s), env)] if that is well-formed;
otherwise, [`D] is [`default_domain].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`[*completion-domain](s)] 为 [`D()]，其中如果表达式
[`get_completion_domain<>(get_env(s), env)] 良构，则 [`D] 是该表达式的退化类型；否则为
[`default_domain]。

[para]
[:en] Let [`[*transformed-sndr](dom, tag, s)] be the expression
[:zh_CN] 若表达式
[codeblock]
dom.transform_sender(tag, s, env)
[codeblock:end]
[:en@~] if that expression is well-formed; otherwise,
[:zh_CN] 良构，则令 [`[*transformed-sndr](dom, tag, s)] 为该表达式；否则令其为
[codeblock]
default_domain().transform_sender(tag, s, env)
[codeblock:end]

[:en] Let [`[*transform-recurse](dom, tag, s)] be the expression
[`[*transformed-sndr](dom, tag, s)] if [`[*transformed-sndr](dom, tag, s)] and [`s]
have the same type ignoring cv-qualifiers; otherwise, it is
the expression [`[*transform-recurse](dom2, tag, s2)], where
[`s2] is [`[*transformed-sender](dom, tag, s)] and
[`dom2] is [*start-domain] if [`tag] is [`start], and
[`[*completion-domain](s2)] otherwise.
[:zh_CN] 令 [`[*transform-recurse](dom, tag, s)] 为表达式
[`[*transformed-sndr](dom, tag, s)]，如果表达式 [`[*transformed-sndr](dom, tag, s)]
和 [`s] 忽略 cv 限定符具有相同类型；否则，令其为表达式 [`[*transform-recurse](dom2, tag, s2)]，
其中 [`s2] 为 [`[*transformed-sender](dom, tag, s)]，而 [`dom2] 当 [`tag] 为
[`start] 时为 [*start-domain]，否则为 [`[*completion-domain](s2)]。

[:en] Let [*tmp-sndr] be the expression
[:zh_CN] 令 [*tmp-sndr] 为表达式
[codeblock]
[[redoc("*>")]]transform-recurse([[redoc("*>")]]completion-domain(sndr), set_value, sndr)
[codeblock:end]
[:en@~] and let [*final-sndr] be the expression
[:zh_CN@~] 并令 [*final-sndr] 为表达式
[codeblock]
[[redoc("*>")]]transform-recurse([[redoc("*>")]]start-domain, start, [[redoc("*>")]]tmp-sndr)
[codeblock:end]

[para:returns]
[:en] [*final-sndr].
[:zh_CN] [*final-sndr]。

[para:remarks]
[:en] The exception specification is equivalent to [`noexcept([*final-sndr])].
[:zh_CN] 异常说明等价于 [`noexcept([*final-sndr])]
[div:end]
